Text.string: Target in sight, time to fire!
Let's see what you got, grunt!
You're even dumber than you look, assassin!
Medic! Get the hell over here.
Eat it, you damn Vault Hunters!
Yeaaah! Check out this flank action!
Y'all are dyin' WAY TOO QUICK!
Could use a frickin' hand here!
I can fly! I can fly!
Looks like you stepped in something! Oh, just a puddle of your own BLOOD! Nailed it!
Hit the deck! He's gonna blow!
He's a goner -- hit the deck!
Pack fire -- get out of here!
You'll lose the battle AND the war!
Come on! Show me what you got!
This is gonna be a bloodbath!
MAL, send me some REAL competition!
THIS is the big, bad Vault Hunter?
You want some of this, Vaulter?
Looks like we got ourselves a firefight!
Remember your training! Center of mass!
This is my position! There are many like it, but this one is mine!
Where in the name of Maliwan...?
The bot cloaked. Repeat, the bot cloaked!
Get it off! GET IT OFF!
What the hell's wrong with that thing?
Oh crap -- don't eat me, don't eat me!
Oh damn... that looks frickin' mean!
Didn't see this in the briefing!
Gah! Get it off, GET IT OFF!
Eyes up! He's got air support!
What do we do about that?!
Be deadly, damn it! And whatever you do, don't NOT be deadly!
You people are a disgrace to Maliwan!
And they said fencing was for nerds!
You're even worse than I thought.
Thought you were supposed to be tough.
Yeah, that's about what I expected!
What's that, boy? My gun says you suck!
Oh, Captain Dickhead! I didn't see you there.
Put one on the big board!
How do YOU see this going?
Hail to the freakin' champ over here!
I'm gonna be the one to take you down!
I swear by this shield, I will END YOU!
Looks like you ain't as tough as you thought, huh?
That's right. I'm the one who got ya!
Back-up! Now let's trash these Vaulters!
What took you all so damn long?
I'm dyin' here, MAL. Shield me!
Need a shield, pronto! Pronto means NOW!
Where do you think you're goin'?
I can do this all day!
I'm over here! Come and get it!
I challenge YOU! Ha. Come and get me!
You ready for this? I am.
Check it out! Flip. Catch. Nailed it.
I've got like a million of these things.
Wish this was a Tediore sword!
